    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
