    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> dried oregano </strong>and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with the juice of your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>peri peri sauce</strong></p>",
