    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>veg stock</strong></p>",
