    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>peri peri sauce</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>veg stock</strong>, and cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>peri peri pasta sauce</strong></p>",
