    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce is done, add the <strong>baked feta</strong>,<strong> charred pepper</strong> and <strong>drained farfalle</strong> to the <strong>peri peri pasta sauce</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce begins to stick to the<strong> </strong>pasta – this is you <strong>baked feta & peri peri farfalle</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the starchy pasta water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
