      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> baked feta & peri peri farfalle </strong>with the <strong>washed</strong> <strong>rocket</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
